#| msgid "Silverblue filesystem layout"
msgid "{variant-name} filesystem layout"
msgstr "Silverblue 文件系统组织结构"

#. type: Plain text
#: pages/technical-information.adoc:31
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "On Silverblue, the root filesystem is immutable. This means that `/`, `/"
#| "usr` and everything below it is read-only."
msgid ""
"On {variant-name}, the root filesystem is immutable.  This means that `/`, `/"
"usr` and everything below it is read-only."
msgstr ""
"在 Silverblue，根目录是不可变的。也就是说 `/`、`/usr` 和这些目录下的所有文件"
"都是只读的。"

#. type: Plain text
#: pages/technical-information.adoc:35
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "`/var` is where all of Silverblue's runtime state is stored. Symlinks are "
#| "used to make traditional state-carrying directories available in their "
#| "expected locations. This includes:"
